{
  "id": "adv_group_thrx_04_05",
  "title": "IIIX 04 05",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "まず最初に超疑問なんですけど～\nなんで星見プロの人がここにいるんですか～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First of all‚ I’m super curious~\nWhy is someone from Hoshimi Production here~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYの運営が刷新されて\n私が使いっ走りに駆り出されてるからですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The I-UNITY management has been revamped‚\nand I’m being run ragged as an errand boy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "あら、それは大変ですね。ご愁傷様です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh my‚ that sounds tough. My condolences.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "誰のせいだと思っているんですか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whose fault do you think this is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "事務所と姫野さんのせいでしょ？　バカでも知ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s the agency and Himeno-san’s fault‚ right? Even an idiot knows that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それもありますが……\nここに来たそもそもの原因は、あなた達が――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s part of it‚ but…\nBut the real reason I’m here is because you――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYの表彰式には出ない、なんて\n言い出すからです。どういうことですか？　理由は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Said you wouldn’t attend the I-UNITY awards ceremony.\nWhat does that mean? What’s the reason?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "……だって必要ないでしょう？　二位の称号なんて\n私達はスリクス……BIG4の一角なんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Because there’s no need‚ right? For a second-place title or anything.\nWe’re ⅢX… one of the BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "……まっ、今となっては元、だけどね。知らないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well‚ it’s a thing of the past now. I don’t know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "まだ確定じゃないでしょ。とにかく……\n優勝以外は無価値なんですよ、私達にとっては",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not confirmed yet. Anyway…\nAnything other than first place is worthless to us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "その上昇志向と理屈には、一定の理解は示します\nだけど、それは結局……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can understand that kind of ambition and reasoning to a certain extent.\nBut in the end…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "自分達を負かしたサニーピースから\n逃げてるだけなんじゃありませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn’t it just running away\nfrom Sunny Peace‚ who defeated you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "はあ！？　そんなんじゃないし！\nつーか、そんなやっすい挑発、乗ると思ってんの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!? That’s not true!\nAnd what‚ do you think we're gonna fall for such a cheap provocation?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "そのリアクションは乗ってるうちに入るわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That reaction falls under the category of being provoked.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "揚げ足とんな！　どっちの味方なわけ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t nitpick! Whose side are you on!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "はあ、もう……ほんと、みっともない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh‚ that’s enough… It’s so embarrassing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あー……すみません、私はそろそろ失礼します\nまたお会いすることがありましたら、その時はよろしく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… Sorry‚ I’ll be taking my leave now.\nIf we meet again‚ please take care of me then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "……ええ、機会がありましたら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes‚ if the opportunity arises.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "（それから間もなく、予想されていた通り）\n（プレタポルテの、アイドル事業からの撤退が決まった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Not long after that‚ as expected‚）\n（Pret-A-Porter’s withdrawal from the idol business was decided.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "（同時に、私達もプレタポルテを退所）\n（フリーでアイドル活動を続けることになった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（At the same time‚ we also left Pret-A-Porter）\n（and decided to continue our idol activities as freelancers.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4733.333333399997,
          "startTime": 122.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "はあ、フリーで活動……言うのは簡単で\n実際にやるのは大変だと、覚悟はしていたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh‚ freelance work… It’s easy to say‚\nbut I was prepared for it to be difficult in practice…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "だから、都内はテナントの家賃が高いのよ！\n個人事務所なんだから、経費削れるところは削らないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why rent for office space is so expensive in the city!\nSince it’s a personal office‚ we have to cut costs where we can.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "だからって茨城に芸能事務所はないでしょ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there are no entertainment agencies in Ibaraki!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_04_05-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "あなた茨城を馬鹿にしたわね！？\n都内との交通の便がいい地区もあるし、何より安いし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You just insulted Ibaraki!?\nThere are areas with good access to the city‚ and it’s cheap above all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.4333333333,
